		<div class="columnContent">
			<h2>Paypal Subscriptions Plug-in for Wordpress MU - v2.0</h2>

			<h3>Pay to Blog</h3>
			<p>
				Monetize your Wordpress MU website with this plug-in.  WP Subscriber allows you to charge
				your blog owners subscription fees.  Simply create your Paypal subscription buttons at
				the Paypal website and paste the code into the plug-in's admin forms.  Offer as many
				subscription choices as you'd like.
			</p>

			<h3>Affiliate Management Built-in</h3>
			<p>
				Turn your subscribers into your best sales people.  You have the option of offering
				flat or percentage affiliate commissions to subscribers that bring additional subscribers to your Wordpress
				MU website.
			</p>

			<div id="media">
				<div id="noUpdate">
